---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | Mikael Johansson"
  description="Background, experience, and focus across SEO, web engineering, automation, and AI-assisted workflows."
  lang="en"
>
  <div class="home-shell">
    <section class="band band--surface" aria-labelledby="about-title">
      <header class="section-head reveal-block">
        <p class="section-kicker">Profile</p>
        <h1 id="about-title" class="section-title">Background and focus</h1>
        <p class="section-lead">
          I have worked with SEO and web engineering since 2003, in roles such as specialist, product owner,
          agency lead, and technical owner. In parallel, I am training to work as a professional truck driver.
          My strength is combining strategy with implementation.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2">
        <article class="ui-card ui-card--interactive reveal-card p-6 text-left" tabindex="0">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Short summary</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-neutral-300">
            I have built and led SEO and growth operations in both agency and in-house environments,
            while developing custom solutions across e-commerce, content, and automation.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-300">
            Over the years I have worked internationally, led teams and processes, and built
            technical systems that can scale and evolve.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-300">
            At the same time, I am building transport competence with focus on heavy vehicle handling, safety, and operational discipline.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="ui-card ui-card--interactive reveal-card p-6 text-left" tabindex="0">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Current focus</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-neutral-300">
            Technical SEO, information architecture, web engineering, and automation between systems.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-300">
            I also actively use AI tools and prompt design to improve analysis,
            production, and operational workflows.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-3">
        <article class="ui-card ui-card--interactive reveal-card p-5 text-left" tabindex="0">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.18em] text-cyan-300">2003 - present</p>
          <h3 class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold text-white">SEO & web engineering</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-300">Continuous hands-on experience in practical SEO work and technical implementation.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="ui-card ui-card--interactive reveal-card p-5 text-left" tabindex="0">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.18em] text-cyan-300">Agency + In-house</p>
          <h3 class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold text-white">Broad role background</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-300">Experience from specialist execution to leadership, product responsibility, and founder roles.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="ui-card ui-card--interactive reveal-card p-5 text-left" tabindex="0">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.18em] text-cyan-300">AI + Automation</p>
          <h3 class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold text-white">Modern delivery model</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-300">AI support, automation, and measurable follow-up in the same workflow.</p>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
        <a
          href="/en/cv"
          class="btn-primary inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 text-sm focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-cyan-200 focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-neutral-950"
        >
          Open full CV
          <span aria-hidden="true">-&gt;</span>
        </a>
        <a
          href="/en/projects"
          class="btn-secondary inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 text-sm focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-white/70 focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-neutral-950"
        >
          View projects
          <span aria-hidden="true">-&gt;</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
